  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Relevant Advertising We may use demographic and preference information to allow advertising on the NYT Service to be targeted to the users for whom they are most pertinent This means users see advertising that is most likely to interest them and advertisers send their messages to people who are most likely to be receptive improving both the viewer s experience and the effectiveness of the ads We disclose information to third parties only in aggregate or de-identified form</evidence>
